  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study proposes to compare specialized closure devices to achieve hemostasis with the&#xD;
      Figure-of-eight suture technique.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Procedures where patients requiring large bore venous access will be randomized 1:1 to either&#xD;
      the Figure-of-eight suture technique or the Perclose Device to achieve hemostasis.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
